526
00:44:26,070 --> 00:44:28,865
Kau pasti muak karena sudah menulis
banyak dongeng.

527
00:44:29,324 --> 00:44:33,453
Bagaimana kalau kita ganti genre lain?

528
00:44:36,205 --> 00:44:39,959
Ya. Kita bisa coba genre
yang sesuai kepribadianmu.

529
00:44:40,084 --> 00:44:43,421
Bagaimana dengan novel kejahatan
atau pembunuhan?

530
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:47,383
Horor, seni bela diri, cinta tragis?

531
00:44:48,426 --> 00:44:49,260
Atau…

532
00:44:49,594 --> 00:44:50,845
Novel dewasa?

533
00:44:50,928 --> 00:44:51,846
Berhenti selamanya.

534
00:44:52,430 --> 00:44:54,015
Aku tak akan menulis lagi.

535
00:44:54,098 --> 00:44:57,018
Aku hanya akan bermain sampai aku mati.

536
00:44:57,977 --> 00:45:00,688
Tidak. Jangan begitu, Mun-yeong.

537
00:45:01,314 --> 00:45:02,523
Ini…

538
00:45:03,649 --> 00:45:07,236
Kau hanya terkejut karena masalah ini.

539
00:45:08,112 --> 00:45:09,989
Istirahatlah selama satu tahun…

540
00:45:10,114 --> 00:45:11,157
Pak Lee.

541
00:45:17,497 --> 00:45:18,539
Aku

542
00:45:19,499 --> 00:45:21,834
